a|\u8b58\u6cd5\u4ee3\u8a00\u4eba]]\u300b||Suen Man-Yee<br>\u5b6b\u654f\u5100\n|-\n| ''[[Glittering Days (TV series)|Glittering Days]]''<br>\u300a[[:zh:\u6771\u65b9\u4e4b\u73e0|\u6771\u65b9\u4e4b\u73e0]]\u300b||Gam Yin<br>\u91d1\u71d5\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\" | 2008 || ''[[Wars of In-Laws II]]''<br>\u300a[[:zh:\u91ce\u883b\u5976\u5976\u5927\u6230\u6208\u5e2b\u5976|\u91ce\u883b\u5976\u5976\u5927\u6230\u6208\u5e2b\u5976]]\u300b|| Gwo Bik<br>\u6208\u78a7\n|-\n| ''[[When Easterly Showers Fall on the Sunny West]]'' <br> \u300a[[:zh:\u6771\u5c71\u98c4\u96e8\u897f\u95dc\u6674|\u6771\u5c71\u98c4\u96e8\u897f\u95dc\u6674]]\u300b || Chong Fung-yi<br>\u838a\u9cf3\u5100\n|-\n| 2010 || ''[[OL Supreme]]'' <br> \u5973\u738b\u8fa6\u516c\u5ba4 || Lui Siu-fung<br>\u96f7\u5c0f\u9cf3 \n|-\n| 2010\u20132011|| ''[[Home Troopers]]''<br>\u300a[[:zh:\u5c45\u5bb6\u5175\u5718|\u5c45\u5bb6\u5175\u5718]]\u300b||Lai Ka-ka<br>\u9ece\u5609\u5609\n|-\n| 2011 || ''[[Super Snoops]]''<br>\u300a[[:zh:\u8343\u52a0\u798f\u797f\u58fd\u63a2\u6848|\u8343\u52a0\u798f\u797f\u58fd\u63a2\u6848]]\u300b || Sun Chiu-tung<br>\u8f9b\u6f6e\u5f64 \n|-\n| 2012 || ''[[Divas in Distress]]''<br>\u300a[[:zh:\u5df4\u4e0d\u5f97\u5abd\u5abd|\u5df4\u4e0d\u5f97\u5abd\u5abd]]\u300b||Sheung Ying-hung<br>\u5546\u6620\u7d05\n|-\n| 2014 || ''[[Come On, Cousin]]'' <br>\u8001\u8868\uff0c\u4f60\u597dhea\uff01 || Herself \n|-\n|rowspan=2| 2015 || ''[[Limelight Years]]'' <br> \u83ef\u9e97\u8f49\u8eab || Wah Fong-ying  <br>\u83ef\u82b3\u51dd \n|-\n| ''[[Master of Destiny]]''<br> \u98a8\u96f2\u5929\u5730 ||Kwan Yeuk-nam<br>\u95dc\u82e5\u7537\n|-\n|rowspan=2| 2018 || ''[[Heart and Greed]]'' <br> \u6e8f\u5fc3\u98ce\u66b43 || Heung Ching Yi <br> \u5411\u6e05\u6c82 \n|-\n| ''[[My Ages Apart]]'' <br> \u8a87\u4e16\u4ee3 || Sheung Hing Chong <br> \u5c1a\u6176\u838a \n|}\n\n=== Films ===\n* ''Singing Darlings'' (1969)\n* ''Miss Not Home'' (1970)\n* ''The Sausage Chase'' (1978)\n* ''Full Moon Scimitar'' (1979)\n* ''ATM'' (2015)\n\n<ref>[http://hkmdb.com/db/people/view.mhtml?id=3636&display_set=eng Liza Wang at hkmdb.com]</ref>\n<ref>[http://chinesemov.com/actors/Liza%20Wang.html Liza Wang at chinesemov.com]</ref>\n\n==Acting awards==\n{| border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 90%;\"\n|- bgcolor=\"#B0C4DE\" align=\"center\"\n!Year\n!Award\n!Category\n!Series\n!Result\n|-\n|1999||TVB Anniversary Awards||All-Time Most Memorable Female Leading Roles||''A House is not a Home''||{{won}}\n|-\n|2000||TVB Anniversary Awards||My Favourite Television Character||''[[At the Threshold of an Era II]]''||{{won}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|2001||rowspan=\"2\"|TVB Anniversary Awards||[[TVB Anniversary Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]]||rowspan=\"2\"|''[[The Awakening Story]]''||{{won}}\n|-\n|My Favourite Television Character||{{won}}\n|-\n|2005||TVB Anniversary Awards||[[TVB Anniversary Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]]||''[[War of In-Laws]]''||{{won}}\n|-\n|2010||TVB Anniversary Awards||Best Host||''Fun With Liza and Gods''||{{won}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|2015||rowspan=\"2\"|Starhub TVB Awards||Best Actress||''Limelight Years''||{{won}}\n|-\n|Best Host||''Sunday Songbird||{{won}}\n|-\n|}\n\n==Honors==\n* [[Silver Bauhinia Star]] (2004)<ref name=SBS/>\n* TVB Best Actress (2001, 2005)\n* RTHK Gold Needle Award (2005)\n* Mont Blanc de la Culture International Award (2007)\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category|Liza Wang}}\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20120114154120/http://www.lizawang.com/ Official Liza Wang web-site]\n*[http://www.lizawang.com/touch/forum.asp Official Liza Wang Forum]\n\n{{s-start}} \t \n{{s-ach}}\n|-\n! colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#DAA520;\" | [[TVB Anniversary Awards]]\n{{succession box\n| title=Best Actress\n| years=2001<br>'''for ''[[The Awakening Story]]'' '''\n| before=[[Carol Cheng]]<br>for ''War of the Genders''\n| after=[[Flora Chan]]<br>for ''[[Fam